pull_request.title: Add missing OQS_ENABLE_SHA3_xkcp_low_avx2 line to oqsconfig.h
pull_request.body: Fixes a missing #define, which is causing the loss of performance for Frodo and Kyber on https://github.com/open-quantum-safe/profiling/issues/47.

pull_request.title: OpenSSH 8.4
pull_request.body:
The skipped tests are listed [here](https://github.com/open-quantum-safe/openssh/blob/openssh-8/oqs-test/run_tests.sh#L9), with respect to the ones to investigate, I didn't have the time to fix them or determine which among them are high priority.

CI testing commands are [here](https://github.com/open-quantum-safe/openssh/blob/openssh-8/.circleci/config.yml#L40).

TODO items can be found by grepping for `OQS-TODO`. The code could also use more cleaning up, and the regression tests could be improved.
